<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <title><%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> - Reproducteurs | Spirit of Freedom Kennel</title>
        <meta name="description" content="Découvrez nos <%= genderPath === 'males' ? 'étalons' : 'femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> au Spirit of Freedom Kennel : reproducteurs d'exception soigneusement sélectionnés pour leurs qualités morphologiques, leur santé et leur tempérament. Élevage à Codognan, dans le Gard.">
        <meta name="keywords" content="<%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalon' : 'femelle' %> <%= currentBreed.toLowerCase() %> gard, <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'mâle' : 'femelle' %> <%= currentBreed.toLowerCase() %> codognan, reproducteur <%= currentBreed.toLowerCase() %> FBKC ABKC, <%= currentBreed.toLowerCase() %> <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalon saillie' : 'reproductrice' %> spirit of freedom kennel">
        <meta name="author" content="Spirit of Freedom Kennel">
        <meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1">
        <meta name="googlebot" content="index, follow">
        <link rel="canonical" href="https://spiritoffreedomkennel.com/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>">
        <meta name="language" content="fr">
        <meta name="geo.region" content="FR-30">
        <meta name="geo.placename" content="Codognan, Gard">
        <meta property="og:type" content="website">
        <meta property="og:site_name" content="Spirit of Freedom Kennel">
        <meta property="og:title" content="<%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> - Spirit of Freedom Kennel">
        <meta property="og:description" content="Nos <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalons' : 'femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> d'exception au Spirit of Freedom Kennel : reproducteurs sélectionnés avec soin, conformes aux standards ABKC et FBKC.">
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://spiritoffreedomkennel.com/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>">
        <meta property="og:image" content="https://spiritoffreedomkennel.com/img/og/og-image.webp">
        <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
        <meta property="og:image:height" content="630">
        <meta property="og:image:alt" content="<%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> - Spirit of Freedom Kennel">
        <meta property="og:locale" content="fr_FR">
        <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
        <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> - Spirit of Freedom Kennel">
        <meta name="twitter:description" content="Nos <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalons' : 'femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %> d'exception au Spirit of Freedom Kennel, à Codognan dans le Gard.">
        <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://spiritoffreedomkennel.com/img/og/og-image.webp">
        <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Spirit of Freedom Kennel - <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %>">
        <%- include('../front/partials/head-meta-base.ejs') %>
        <%- include('../front/partials/head-fonts-libs.ejs') %>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/front/css/navbar.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/front/css/chiens.css">
    </head>
    <body class="h-100">
        <%- include('../front/frontEndAssets/header') %>
        <main style="padding-top: 70px;">
            <section class="page-intro-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="specialty-text">
                        <div class="specialty-box-inline">
                            <div class="specialty-top-bar"></div>
                            <div class="specialty-grid">
                                <div class="specialty-main">
                                    <h1 class="specialty-title">
                                        <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <span class="text-gold"><%= currentBreed %></span>
                                    </h1>
                                    <% if (currentGender === 'Male') { %>
                                    <p>Découvrez la sélection de nos étalons <strong><%= currentBreed %></strong> présent au sein de l'élevage Spirit of Freedom Kennel. Chaque mâle a été choisi pour sa structure athlétique, sa génétique vérifiée et sa parfaite adéquation aux critères des standards de la race.</p>
                                    <p>Fiers représentants de leur race, nos étalons <strong><%= currentBreed %></strong> sont le résultat d'années de sélection rigoureuse sur des lignées internationales d'exception, pour produire des sujets alliant type, santé et caractère.</p>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                    <p>Nos femelles <strong><%= currentBreed %></strong> constituent le socle de notre programme d'élevage au Spirit of Freedom Kennel. Chacune est retenue pour sa morphologie irréprochable, sa stabilité comportementale et ses aptitudes reproductrices.</p>
                                    <p>Issues de lignées soigneusement étudiées, elles garantissent des portées de qualité, conformes aux exigences des standards ABKC et FBKC, dans le respect du bien-être animal.</p>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="dog-filters-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="dog-filters-desktop">
                        <a href="/chiens" class="dog-filter-btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-paw me-2"></i>Toutes les races
                        </a>
                        <% races.forEach(race => { %>
                        <a href="/chiens/<%= race.breed_slug %>"
                            class="dog-filter-btn <%= race.breed_slug === currentBreedSlug ? 'active' : '' %>">
                        <%= race.breed_name %>
                        </a>
                        <% }); %>
                        <div class="dog-filter-separator"></div>
                        <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/males"
                            class="dog-filter-btn male <%= genderPath === 'males' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                        <i class="fas fa-mars me-2"></i>Mâles <%= currentBreed %>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/femelles"
                            class="dog-filter-btn female <%= genderPath === 'femelles' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                        <i class="fas fa-venus me-2"></i>Femelles <%= currentBreed %>
                        </a>
                        <div class="dog-filter-separator"></div>
                        <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/saillies" class="dog-filter-btn saillie">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart me-2"></i>Saillies <%= currentBreed %>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dog-filters-mobile">
                        <button class="dog-filters-toggle" id="dogFiltersToggle">
                            <div class="dog-filters-toggle-left">
                                <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
                                <span>Filtrer les chiens</span>
                            </div>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="dog-filters-menu" id="dogFiltersMenu">
                            <a href="/chiens" class="dog-filter-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-paw me-2"></i>Toutes les races
                            </a>
                            <% races.forEach(race => { %>
                            <a href="/chiens/<%= race.breed_slug %>"
                                class="dog-filter-item <%= race.breed_slug === currentBreedSlug ? 'active' : '' %>">
                            <i class="fas fa-dog me-2"></i><%= race.breed_name %>
                            </a>
                            <% }); %>
                            <div class="dog-filter-divider"></div>
                            <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/males"
                                class="dog-filter-item male <%= genderPath === 'males' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                            <i class="fas fa-mars me-2"></i>Mâles <%= currentBreed %>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/femelles"
                                class="dog-filter-item female <%= genderPath === 'femelles' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                            <i class="fas fa-venus me-2"></i>Femelles <%= currentBreed %>
                            </a>
                            <div class="dog-filter-divider"></div>
                            <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/saillies" class="dog-filter-item saillie">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart me-2"></i>Saillies <%= currentBreed %>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="dog-grid-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <% if (animals && animals.length > 0) { %>
                    <div class="breed-section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="breed-section-header-left">
                            <span class="label-tag"><%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %> <%= currentBreed %></span>
                            <h2 class="breed-section-title">
                                Nos <span class="text-gold"><%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'Étalons' : 'Femelles' %></span> <%= currentBreed %>
                            </h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breed-gallery-counter">
                            <span class="counter-number"><%= totalItems %></span>
                            <span class="counter-label"><%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalons' : 'femelles' %></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <% animals.forEach((animal, index) => { %>
                        <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="<%= index * 50 %>">
                            <article class="dog-card">
                                <div class="dog-card-image">
                                    <%
                                        let animalImageSrc;
                                        if (animal.optimized_image_path) {
                                            animalImageSrc = '/uploads/optimized/' + animal.optimized_image_path;
                                        } else if (animal.image_path) {
                                            animalImageSrc = '/uploads/' + animal.image_path;
                                        } else {
                                            animalImageSrc = '/img/placeholder-dog.jpg';
                                        }
                                        %>
                                    <a href="/chiens/<%= animal.breed_slug %>/<%= animal.slug %>">
                                    <img src="<%= animalImageSrc %>"
                                        alt="<%= animal.balise_alt || animal.name %>"
                                        onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/img/placeholder-dog.jpg';">
                                    </a>
                                    <div class="dog-gender-badge <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'male' : 'female' %>">
                                        <i class="fas <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'fa-mars' : 'fa-venus' %>"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dog-card-body">
                                    <div class="dog-card-top-bar"></div>
                                    <h3 class="dog-card-name">
                                        <a href="/chiens/<%= animal.breed_slug %>/<%= animal.slug %>"><%= animal.name %></a>
                                    </h3>
                                    <div class="dog-card-race">
                                        <i class="fas fa-paw"></i>
                                        <a href="/chiens/<%= animal.breed_slug %>"><%= animal.breed_name %></a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="dog-card-info">
                                        <% if (animal.breed_type) { %>
                                        <div class="dog-info-item">
                                            <i class="fas fa-dog"></i>
                                            <span><%= animal.breed_type %></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <% } %>
                                        <% if (animal.color) { %>
                                        <div class="dog-info-item">
                                            <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                                            <span><%= animal.color %></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <% } %>
                                        <% if (animal.eye_color) { %>
                                        <div class="dog-info-item">
                                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                            <span><%= animal.eye_color %></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <% } %>
                                        <% if (animal.register_name) { %>
                                        <div class="dog-info-item">
                                            <i class="fas fa-certificate"></i>
                                            <span><%= animal.register_name %></span>
                                        </div>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </div>
                                    <a href="/chiens/<%= animal.breed_slug %>/<%= animal.slug %>" class="btn-view-dog-card">
                                    Voir le profil <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <div class="text-center py-5" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="no-dogs-message">
                            <i class="fas fa-paw fa-3x mb-4" style="color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3)"></i>
                            <h3>Aucun chien disponible</h3>
                            <p>Aucun <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalon' : 'femelle' %> <strong><%= currentBreed %></strong> ne correspond à vos critères</p>
                            <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>" class="btn-back-dogs">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Voir tous les <%= currentBreed %>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </section>
            <% if (totalPages > 1) { %>
            <section class="dog-pagination-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <nav aria-label="Navigation pagination" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <ul class="dog-pagination">
                            <% if (currentPage > 1) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>?page=<%= currentPage - 1 %>" class="dog-pagination-link prev">
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
                                <span>Précédent</span>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                            <%
                                let startPage = Math.max(1, currentPage - 2);
                                let endPage = Math.min(totalPages, currentPage + 2);
                                
                                if (startPage > 1) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>?page=1" class="dog-pagination-link">1</a>
                            </li>
                            <% if (startPage > 2) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <span class="dog-pagination-dots">...</span>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                            <% } %>
                            <% for (let i = startPage; i <= endPage; i++) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>?page=<%= i %>"
                                    class="dog-pagination-link <%= i === currentPage ? 'active' : '' %>">
                                <%= i %>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (endPage < totalPages) { %>
                            <% if (endPage < totalPages - 1) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <span class="dog-pagination-dots">...</span>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>?page=<%= totalPages %>" class="dog-pagination-link">
                                <%= totalPages %>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (currentPage < totalPages) { %>
                            <li class="dog-pagination-item">
                                <a href="/chiens/<%= currentBreedSlug %>/<%= genderPath %>?page=<%= currentPage + 1 %>" class="dog-pagination-link next">
                                <span>Suivant</span>
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <% } %>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                    <div class="dog-pagination-info" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                        Page <strong><%= currentPage %></strong> sur <strong><%= totalPages %></strong>
                        (<%= totalItems %> <%= currentGender === 'Male' ? 'étalon(s)' : 'femelle(s)' %> <%= currentBreed %> au total)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <% } %>
            <section class="dog-cta-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="dog-cta-box" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="dog-cta-left">
                            <span class="label-tag">Intéressé ?</span>
                            <h2 class="dog-cta-title">Votre futur compagnon <span class="text-gold">vous attend</span></h2>
                            <p class="dog-cta-text">Contactez-nous pour en savoir plus sur nos reproducteurs, nos saillies disponibles et nos chiots FBKC & ABKC à venir.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="dog-cta-right">
                            <a href="/chiots" class="btn-dog-cta-secondary">
                            <i class="fas fa-paw me-2"></i>Voir les chiots
                            </a>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-dog-cta-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Nous contacter
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../front/frontEndAssets/footer') %>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="/front/js/header.js"></script>
        <%- include('./partials/googleAnalytics') %>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
        <script>
            AOS.init({
                duration: 1000,
                easing: "ease-in-out",
                once: true,
                offset: 120,
                delay: 0,
                anchorPlacement: "top-bottom",
                mirror: false,
                disable: "mobile",
            });
        </script>
        <script>
            document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
                const toggleBtn = document.getElementById("dogFiltersToggle");
                const menu = document.getElementById("dogFiltersMenu");
            
                if (toggleBtn && menu) {
                    toggleBtn.addEventListener("click", function () {
                        menu.classList.toggle("active");
                        toggleBtn.classList.toggle("active");
                    });
                    document.addEventListener("click", function (e) {
                        if (!toggleBtn.contains(e.target) && !menu.contains(e.target)) {
                            menu.classList.remove("active");
                            toggleBtn.classList.remove("active");
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>